p.d: Dresden Dolls have performed at some of the world's biggest festivals including Coachella, Fuji Rock, Roskilde and Glastonbury, and whether you call it theatrical rock, punk cabaret, manic-musical or neo-glam-torch it's a great night out you won't forget. For The Dresden Dolls and their legions of fans life is obviously more than 'just a Cabaret'. - hear it and see it and believe!
